 _______________________________________________________________________
 
 Mandriva Linux Security Advisory                         MDKSA-2006:089
 http://www.mandriva.com/security/
 _______________________________________________________________________
 
 Package : kphone
 Date    : May 24, 2006
 Affected: 2006.0
 _______________________________________________________________________
 
 Problem Description:
 
 Kphone creates .qt/kphonerc with world-readable permissions, which 
 allows local users to read usernames and SIP passwords.
 
 Packages have been patched to correct this issue.
 _______________________________________________________________________

 References:
 
 http://cve.mitre.org/cgi-bin/cvename.cgi?name=CVE-2006-2442
 _______________________________________________________________________
 
